    "title": "Looking for Financial Analyst at Punjab National Bank Consulting Pvt Ltd",
    "description": "Punjab National Bank Consulting Pvt Ltd, one of India's leading organizations, is hiring a Financial Analyst for our Pune operations. We offer a competitive salary package along with world-class benefits.\n\nAbout Punjab National Bank Consulting Pvt Ltd:\nPunjab National Bank Consulting Pvt Ltd is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Prepare and analyze financial statements, reports, and budgets\n• Monitor financial performance against targets and provide variance analysis\n• Maintain general ledger and ensure accurate bookkeeping\n• Manage accounts payable and accounts receivable functions\n• Ensure compliance with tax regulations and statutory requirements\n• Process payroll and manage employee reimbursements\n• Liaise with banks, regulators, and financial institutions\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• BPharm / MPharm / PharmD\n• 1-3 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in SAP FICO\n• Proficiency in Tally\n• Proficiency in Forecasting\n• Proficiency in GST\n• Proficiency in SQL\n• Proficiency in Financial Reporting\n• Proficiency in Risk Management\n• Proficiency in MS Excel\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Referral bonus program\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Salary Range: 4 LPA - 9 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Pune, Maharashtra, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Punjab National Bank Consulting Pvt Ltd!",
